Tread Lightly! is a nonprofit organization in the United States with the mission "to empower generations to enjoy the outdoors responsibly through stewardship to further the goals of responsible and ethical recreation." As a nonprofit, Tread Lightly! is a member-based organization. Individual, small business, corporate and other nonprofit members support and help spread the Tread Lightly! message. With more than 40,000 members and supporters and more than 80 official partners, Tread Lightly! continues to grow and have a more powerful educational impact.
